! Mobile & Tablet Support

The Darts Scoreboard includes comprehensive responsive design for all screen sizes.

!! Mobile Phones (Portrait & Landscape)

* Optimized button sizes and touch targets
* Stacked form controls for easier input
* Compressed scoreboard with readable font sizes
* Full-width buttons for easy tapping
* Efficient use of screen space

!! Tablets

* Balanced layout for both orientations
* Appropriately sized text and controls
* Flexible grid system for the scoreboard
* Room for multiple players on screen
* Comfortable viewing distance

!! Desktop

* Full-featured interface
* Spacious layout
* All statistics visible
* Large scoreboard table
* Keyboard shortcut support

!! Key Responsive Features

* ''Flexible Scoreboard'' - Adapts to screen width automatically
* ''Touch-Friendly Controls'' - Larger tap targets on mobile
* ''Readable Text'' - Font sizes adjust for device
* ''Efficient Space Usage'' - Maximizes content in landscape mode
* ''Scrollable Areas'' - Handle overflow gracefully

!! Small Screen Landscape Mode

Special optimizations for phones in landscape:

* Compact header to maximize content space
* Reduced margins and padding
* Optimized control layout
* Shorter match history panel
* Quick access to key functions

!! Testing Your Device

The scoreboard automatically detects your screen size and adjusts accordingly. Try:

# Rotating your device between portrait and landscape
# Resizing your browser window (desktop)
# Zooming in/out to test readability
# Using touch gestures vs mouse clicks

The interface should remain usable and attractive at all sizes.
